nodes.bodyText: Let's throw an exception if we get this (we shouldn't but be safe)

commit.message:
Remove use of EquatableValueSet from the Iceberg connector

This commit removes use of EquatableValueSet from the Iceberg
connector because the case of EquatableValueSet types doesn't
occur in the Iceberg type system.  The commit adds a check
to ensure that an EquatableValueSet is never passed to
DomainConverter.translateDomain().
